{"id":63238,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/04/vista試玩ipad記/","date":"2010-04-25T05:20:22Z","modified":"2010-04-25T05:20:22Z","title":"Vista試玩iPad記","content":"</p>\n<div>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/vista/4513524159/\" title=\"photo sharing\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2298/4513524159_93596b5f0f.jpg\"></a></p>\n<p>\t<span><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/vista/4513524159/\">Vista和iPad合影</a>, originally uploaded by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/people/vista/\">vista</a>.</span>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t今天很高興有機會可以跟老地方冰果室借到iPad來測試，結果一如預想就愛不釋手啦！</p>\n<p>這絕對不只是「比較大台的iPhone」，整個使用體驗堪以順暢來比擬。無論是打開Safari瀏覽器來上網，或是透過iBooks來看小熊維尼電子書，甚至是玩起賽車遊戲，真的只有「過癮」二字可以形容。</p>\n<p>當然，iPad也不是全然沒有缺點。比方拿久了還是覺得有點沉，需要有個支架可以靠著比較好，當然還有連網功能需要有穩定的Wi-Fi訊號。不過整體來說，iPad給我的感覺還是充滿許多驚喜。</p>\n<p>當然，最重要的還是iPad可以滿足我的需求。現在，就看看何時才有機會入手了（忍）。\n</p>\n<ul>\n<li>No Related Post</li>\n</ul>\n<map name=\"google_ad_map_1056_a8f3921c1f26cead\">\n<area coords=\"1,2,367,28\" href=\"http://imageads.googleadservices.com/pagead/imgclick/1056?pos=0\" shape=\"rect\">\n<area coords=\"384,10,453,23\" href=\"http://services.google.com/feedback/abg\" shape=\"rect\"></map>\n<p><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://imageads.googleadservices.com/pagead/ads?format=468x30_aff_img&amp;client=&amp;channel=&amp;output=png&amp;cuid=1056&amp;url=%20http%3A%2F%2Fblog.vista.tw%2Farchives%2F2010%2F04%2F12%2F1056\" usemap=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/Vista20#google_ad_map_1056_a8f3921c1f26cead\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Vista20?a=5hb-0LnAops:awC9gwNLHas:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Vista20?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\"></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Vista20?a=5hb-0LnAops:awC9gwNLHas:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Vista20?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\"></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Vista20?a=5hb-0LnAops:awC9gwNLHas:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://f